Author: fategghead
Text: I really appreciate it, I’m second guessing myself for it all but I know how much scarier and how much more alone I’ll feel if I keep struggling in silence

Author: chassischuck
Text: ❤❤❤❤ I'm glad you have someone to help you!!   You got this you are bigger than this disorder   You have it   It doesnt have you!  Proud of you!
